How to play!

General:
-Sanitized equipment will reduce spoilage chances.
-Using the mouse and clicking is all you need!


Cider:
-Put any combination of apple into the carboy with a choice of yeast to see what happens!

-Once fermented, drag the siphon tube to the carboy to bottle.


Pickles:
-fill the mason jar with combinations of peppers and cucumber to see what happens. 

-The more salt added the less of a chance of spoilage.

-Use the blender after done fermenting to see what happens.


Soda:
-Before making soda, maintain a ginger bug in a mason jar by feeding it ginger and sugar every day.

-Once ready, use a combo of ingredients to see what sodas are made.
